      <item>
        <title>Global Gem Configuration</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;When changing the gem source with &lt;code&gt;gem source --add &amp;lt;url&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; it only changes in
&lt;code&gt;~/.gemrc&lt;/code&gt; for that user, not globally. Make the change in &lt;code&gt;/etc/gemrc&lt;/code&gt; to make
it global.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
